# Optional: URL of the CompDrift interpretation proxy (Cloudflare Worker).
# When set at build time, the published site can run interpretation WITHOUT the
# visitor providing a key (the Worker holds the key server-side).
#
# This value is NOT a secret — it's a public endpoint and ships in the bundle by design.
# Leave it unset to require each visitor to paste their own Anthropic key.
#
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your deployed Worker URL:
VITE_PROXY_URL=https://compdrift-proxy.YOUR_SUBDOMAIN.workers.dev
